  "instructions": [
    "Place dried apricots in a pot and cover with water. Bring to a boil, reduce heat, and simmer until softened, about 30 minutes.",
    "In the same pot, sauté onion, celery, and bell pepper until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add garlic, coconut milk, vegetable broth, lime juice, coriander seeds, cumin seeds, and salt. Stir well to combine.",
    "Return apricots to the pot along with any liquid. Simmer for another 10-15 minutes or until mixture thickens slightly.",
    "Garnish with fresh cilantro leaves before serving."
